reviewText: Very pleased with item. Delivery was expedited.
This was a gift to a Tennessee Titans & Steve McNair fan and she truly loved it. I had seen it on the NFL Network and I loved it.

Coming from a small town in Mississippi, "Air McNair" had a lot to prove during his college career and especially while in the NFL.  It was very shocking and tragic on how his life ended.  A "must see" for all who gain strength from "the power to overcome".
